	ZdecimalJava
	
	Utility package to process IBM System Z packed and zone deciaml numbers
 	in Java.
	
	Installation:
	
	Place the zdecimal jar file in your CLASSPATH
	
	Extract files from the zdecimal jar file using the jar xf command.
	
	Source code is contained in the jar file.
	
	The class files have been built using Java level 1.4 for
	compatibility. You may rebuild as needed.
	
	The demo.java file contains an example program
	The doc directory contains JavaDoc HTML for the package.
